TKINTER GUI
TKINTER is a GUI user interface  for the pythonn
it is the fastest and easiest way  to create a  GUI application and mostly used for gui application
STEP TO CREATE A GUI application
1. IMPORT THE module tkinter
2. Create a main window 
3. Add any number of widgets to main window
4. Apply the event triggers to the widgets
use the command 
import tkinter
1.  there are two main types of  to create main window
1. TK() to create a main window tkinter provide a method AND
 mainloop() and there is method  know by the name mainloop(),it is  used to run  yor application
